        <description>
            <p>While holding this weapon, you can use a bonus action to speak this weapons command word, causing flames to erupt from it. These flames shed bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet.</p>
        </description>
        <setters>
            <set name="category">Monster Materials</set>
